          <p>PDF forensic reports — police-ready, court-ready. On-chain evidence citations, timeline reconstruction, and recommended actions.</p>
          <a href="/features#le-reports" class="feature-link mono">Explore →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card reveal">
          <div class="feature-icon">◉</div>
