          <span class="uc-num mono">01</span>
          <h3>Law Enforcement</h3>
          <p>Equip investigators with court-admissible forensic reports and real-time wallet surveillance tools.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/use-cases#compliance" class="use-case-card card reveal">
          <span class="uc-num mono">02</span>
          <h3>Compliance & AML</h3>
          <p>Automate suspicious activity detection and generate FIAU-ready reports for regulatory submissions.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/use-cases#fraud" class="use-case-card card reveal">
